raw_data.title: Automation Technician
raw_data.description: Installation, commissioning, maintenance and repair of Honeywell Control systems. Performs installation, maintenance or repair services, checkout and start-up of diverse technologies including, HVAC, Fire & Security, Integrated systems and internet based computer systems. Also possess basic project management and engineering skille to engieer and install small jobs and perform close-out tasks to meet customer requirements.

raw_data.title: Engineering
raw_data.description: Systems design, analysis, installation and integration with a major emphasis on improving system performance to generate savings in energy, operations, and maintenance costs. Specifies system compnents toensure conformance with engineering design and performance specifications. May perform diagnostics and troubleshoots problems as required to resolve system issues and to provide technical information as required. May perform project Management functions as required including developing project plans, directing personnel, and developing procedures for testing and commissioning

raw_data.title: Mechanical Technician
raw_data.description: Provide a wide-range of on call, scheduled preventive maintenance, installation and repair services on HVAC equipment and systems, temperature controls, and energy management systems. Provide proactive preventative maintenance to maintain optimal menchanical system operations to attain desired comfort, safety and operating cost efficiencies
